value.0: This statue depicts Eldath, the Goddess of the Singing Waters. Although shy, quiet and enigmatic, Eldath was possessed of unknown depths of character and unexpressed resolve that could not be broken. Those who reflect upon the statue receive feelings of serenity and comfort.
This well made leather armor was constructed with special materials from the Wealdath, using secrets taught by the nearby elves.

Possibly born of wild magic, this bizzare plant is typically found with corpses at its base. Drawing its nourishment from the blood of the fallen, a Needle Nest can release a barrage of deadly spines against the unsuspecting.
